### Admin login
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@graphify.dev",
  "password": "admin1234"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("adminToken", response.body.data.accessToken);
%}

### GET config
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/admin/openai/config
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### PUT config — 성공
PUT http://localhost:8081/api/v1/admin/openai/config
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "endpointUrl": "https://your-resource.openai.azure.com",
  "apiKey": "test-key-placeholder",
  "deploymentName": "gpt-4o",
  "apiVersion": "2024-02-15",
  "model": "gpt-4o",
  "temperature": 0.3,
  "maxTokens": 4096,
  "topP": 1,
  "embeddingModel": "text-embedding-3-large",
  "embeddingDeployment": "text-embedding-3-large"
}

### PUT config — 실패 (http endpoint)
PUT http://localhost:8081/api/v1/admin/openai/config
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "endpointUrl": "http://invalid.local",
  "deploymentName": "gpt-4o",
  "apiVersion": "2024-02-15",
  "model": "gpt-4o",
  "temperature": 0.3,
  "maxTokens": 4096,
  "topP": 1,
  "embeddingModel": "text-embedding-3-large",
  "embeddingDeployment": "text-embedding-3-large"
}

### GET status
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/admin/openai/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### GET status refresh
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/admin/openai/status?refresh=true
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
